  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869340/extras/0abd2c1c6dd38fdcee9efe94089738c5.avif?t=1770675714\" width=590 height=100 /></span><br>Put it Here is a casual puzzle gameplay that includes item storage, arrangement, packaging, and organization. Players can enjoy the satisfaction and achievement brought by immersively organizing the desktop or stacking and arranging scattered items.<br>Game features:<br><br><br>                           <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869340/extras/5e23c6bce6c941c94d08eeac4dd2908b.poster.avif?t=1770675714\" width=590 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869340/extras/5e23c6bce6c941c94d08eeac4dd2908b.webm?t=1770675714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><br>Discover the laws in the puzzles and arrange them neatly according to certain laws by dragging and dropping items.<br>In the packaging theme, different items are classified and placed and then packaged.<br>A variety of games, a variety of themes and a variety of solutions.<br>Each puzzle has prompts, and you can control the degree of disclosure of the prompts on your own<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869340/extras/3826d100240f743425e0737add2556c9.avif?t=1770675714\" width=590 height=320 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869340/extras/cb7b2387564f166e506e35ffeb242667.avif?t=1770675714\" width=590 height=320 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869340/extras/c11456f93c41e65baa726b4b6e63aa04.avif?t=1770675714\" width=590 height=320 /></span>",
